name: Defel
Lore: 'Male Defel from Af''El. This species, also known as ''wraiths,'' is capable of warping light around themselves, becoming difficult to see at dusk.',
Text: 'Under ''nighttime conditions,'' may use 1 Force to ''hide'' (exclude himself) from a battle. While at a site affected by Revolution, opponent must lose 1 Force during your control phase.',
